<ul><li>DOI: <a href="https://doi.org/10.1145/3426425.3426933">10.1145/3426425.3426933</a></li>
<li><a href="../tag/t1a.html"><span class="tagM">T1A: Design</span></a><ul><li> The main contribution of the paper is to design a language called BabyCobol.
</li></ul></li>
<li><a href="../tag/t3c.html"><span class="tagL">T3C: DSLs</span></a><ul><li> BabyCobol is a domain-specific language.
</li></ul></li>
<li><a href="../tag/t2a.html"><span class="tagL">T2A: Lifecycle</span></a><ul><li> The domain for this language design experience is legacy software.
